57.7	Get	Post/Redirect/Get	Post/Redirect/Get is a web development design pattern that prevents some duplicate form submissions, creating a more intuitive interface for user agents (users). PRG implements bookmarks and the refresh button in a predictable way that does not create duplicate form submissions.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/PostRedirectGet_DoubleSubmitProblem.png/350px-PostRedirectGet_DoubleSubmitProblem.png
